#

Tuna and Avocado Wrap

10 min
$3.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

fishwheat

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carbgluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

quickhealthyno-cook

Description

A refreshing and nutritious wrap filled with creamy avocado and protein-packed tuna, perfect for a quick lunch or snack.

Ingredients

  • whole wheat tortilla: 1 large
  • canned tuna (in water): 1 can (5 oz)
  • ripe avocado: 1 medium
  • mixed greens: 1 cup
  • cherry tomatoes: 5-6
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1/4 teaspoon
